 <H1>Write Lock Scope (3)</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Implications of whole-resource locking:
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Pro: 
<UL>
<LI>Supports existing applications which operate on entire files, providing easy migration path to add WebDAV support
<LI>Handles all content types
</UL><LI>Con:
<UL>
<LI>Reduced availability of resources during collaboration (but, shared locks can helpï¿½)
</UL></UL></UL></P>
